# Vercel Deployment Walkthrough

## Changes Made

### 1. TypeScript Build Error Fixed
**File:** [src/models/Library.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/Library.ts)

The [ILibrary](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/Library.ts#3-15) interface was missing `createdAt` and `updatedAt` fields (added by `timestamps: true` in the schema), causing a type error in the API route.

```diff
  uploaded_by: mongoose.Types.ObjectId;
+ createdAt: Date;
+ updatedAt: Date;
}
```

### 2. [vercel.json](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/vercel.json) Added
**File:** [vercel.json](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/vercel.json)

Configures Vercel to allow API routes up to **30 seconds** (Hobby plan max) to handle MongoDB connection time.

### 3. [.env.example](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/.env.example) Updated
**File:** [.env.example](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/.env.example)

